{"data":[{"name":"78:1","price":"About what are they asking one another?","arabic":"عَمَّ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5673,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿamma yatasāalūna ","translations":["About what","are they asking one another","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿamma","yatasāalūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[2,1240,6345]]}},{"name":"78:2","price":"About the momentous news[1],","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلنَّبَإِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5674,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] i.e., the Resurrection.","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿani al-naba-i al-ʿaẓīmi ","translations":["About","the News","the Great","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿani","al-naba-i","al-ʿaẓīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,490],[2,490,1920],[3,1920,5045]]}},{"name":"78:3","price":"that which they differ about[2].","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي هُمۡ فِيهِ مُخۡتَلِفُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5675,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[2] The pagans of Makkah denied the Qur’an, resurrection, and judgment. They differed as to whether the Qur’an was magic, fortune-telling, or poetry.","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī hum fīhi mukh'talifūna ","translations":["(About) which","they","(are) concerning it","(in) disagreement","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","hum","fīhi","mukh'talifūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,1480],[3,1480,2310],[4,2310,5875]]}},{"name":"78:4","price":"No indeed; they will come to know.","arabic":"كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5676,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā sayaʿlamūna ","translations":["Nay","(soon) they will know","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","sayaʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,3975]]}},{"name":"78:5","price":"Again no; they will come to know.","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5677,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma kallā sayaʿlamūna ","translations":["Then","Nay","(soon) they will know","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","kallā","sayaʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1190],[2,1190,2240],[3,2240,6115]]}},{"name":"78:6","price":"Have We not made the earth a resting place?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ مِهَٰدٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5678,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"alam najʿali al-arḍa mihādan ","translations":["Have not","We made","the earth","a resting place","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","najʿali","al-arḍa","mihādan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,730],[2,730,1220],[3,1220,2600],[4,2600,3915]]}},{"name":"78:7","price":"And the mountains as stakes[3],","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَوۡتَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5679,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[3] Mountains go deep below the surface like pegs and icebergs, stabilizing the earth and slowing tectonic movement.","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-jibāla awtādan ","translations":["And the mountains","(as) pegs","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-jibāla","awtādan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1430],[2,1430,3775]]}},{"name":"78:8","price":"and created you in pairs,","arabic":"وَخَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5680,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wakhalaqnākum azwājan ","translations":["And We created you","(in) pairs","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wakhalaqnākum","azwājan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1940],[2,1940,4045]]}},{"name":"78:9","price":"and made your sleep for rest,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا نَوۡمَكُمۡ سُبَاتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5681,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wajaʿalnā nawmakum subātan ","translations":["And We made","your sleep","(for) rest","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wajaʿalnā","nawmakum","subātan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,2730],[3,2730,4515]]}},{"name":"78:10","price":"and made the night a covering[4],","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلَّيۡلَ لِبَاسٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5682,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[4] Covering you in its darkness as garments cover you.","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wajaʿalnā al-layla libāsan ","translations":["And We made","the night","(as) covering","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wajaʿalnā","al-layla","libāsan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2070],[3,2070,3885]]}},{"name":"78:11","price":"and made the day for seeking a livelihood,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلنَّهَارَ مَعَاشٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5683,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wajaʿalnā al-nahāra maʿāshan ","translations":["And We made","the day","(for) livelihood","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wajaʿalnā","al-nahāra","maʿāshan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1180],[2,1180,3140],[3,3140,4945]]}},{"name":"78:12","price":"and built above you seven mighty heavens,","arabic":"وَبَنَيۡنَا فَوۡقَكُمۡ سَبۡعٗا شِدَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5684,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wabanaynā fawqakum sabʿan shidādan ","translations":["And We constructed","over you","seven","strong","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wabanaynā","fawqakum","sabʿan","shidādan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2630],[3,2630,3670],[4,3670,6275]]}},{"name":"78:13","price":"and made therein a blazing lamp,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا سِرَاجٗا وَهَّاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5685,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wajaʿalnā sirājan wahhājan ","translations":["And We placed","a lamp","burning","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wajaʿalnā","sirājan","wahhājan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[2,1240,2610],[3,2610,5325]]}},{"name":"78:14","price":"and sent down from the rainclouds abundant water,","arabic":"وَأَنزَلۡنَا مِنَ ٱلۡمُعۡصِرَٰتِ مَآءٗ ثَجَّاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5686,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-anzalnā mina al-muʿ'ṣirāti māan thajjājan ","translations":["And We sent down","from","the rain clouds","water","pouring abundantly","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-anzalnā","mina","al-muʿ'ṣirāti","māan","thajjājan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1930],[2,1930,2540],[3,2540,4440],[4,4440,7030],[5,7030,9245]]}},{"name":"78:15","price":"so that We may produce thereby grains and vegetation,","arabic":"لِّنُخۡرِجَ بِهِۦ حَبّٗا وَنَبَاتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5687,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"linukh'rija bihi ḥabban wanabātan ","translations":["That We may bring forth","thereby","grain","and vegetation","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["linukh'rija","bihi","ḥabban","wanabātan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,1810],[3,1810,3290],[4,3290,5235]]}},{"name":"78:16","price":"and gardens with dense foliage?","arabic":"وَجَنَّٰتٍ أَلۡفَافًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5688,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wajannātin alfāfan ","translations":["And gardens","(of) thick foliage","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["wajannātin","alfāfan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2200],[2,2200,4115]]}},{"name":"78:17","price":"Indeed, the Day of Judgment is a time appointed,","arabic":"إِنَّ يَوۡمَ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ كَانَ مِيقَٰتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5689,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"inna yawma al-faṣli kāna mīqātan ","translations":["Indeed","(the) Day","(of) the Judgment","is","an appointed time","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","yawma","al-faṣli","kāna","mīqātan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1890],[3,1890,2920],[4,2920,3530],[5,3530,5635]]}},{"name":"78:18","price":"the Day when the Trumpet will be blown, you will come forth in crowds,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يُنفَخُ فِي ٱلصُّورِ فَتَأۡتُونَ أَفۡوَاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5690,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yunfakhu fī al-ṣūri fatatūna afwājan ","translations":["(The) Day","(in which) shall be blown","in","the trumpet","and you will come forth","(in) crowds","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yunfakhu","fī","al-ṣūri","fatatūna","afwājan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,2190],[3,2190,2360],[4,2360,3390],[5,3390,4880],[6,4880,6855]]}},{"name":"78:19","price":"and the sky will be opened up and will become gateways,","arabic":"وَفُتِحَتِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ فَكَانَتۡ أَبۡوَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5691,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wafutiḥati al-samāu fakānat abwāban ","translations":["And is opened","the heaven","and becomes","gateways","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wafutiḥati","al-samāu","fakānat","abwāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1180],[2,1180,3790],[3,3790,5050],[4,5050,7055]]}},{"name":"78:20","price":"and the mountains will vanish, becoming like a mirage.","arabic":"وَسُيِّرَتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ فَكَانَتۡ سَرَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5692,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wasuyyirati al-jibālu fakānat sarāban ","translations":["And are moved","the mountains","and become","a mirage","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wasuyyirati","al-jibālu","fakānat","sarāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1470],[2,1470,2750],[3,2750,3900],[4,3900,5725]]}},{"name":"78:21","price":"Indeed, Hell is lying in wait,","arabic":"إِنَّ جَهَنَّمَ كَانَتۡ مِرۡصَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5693,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"inna jahannama kānat mir'ṣādan ","translations":["Indeed","Hell","is","lying in wait","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","jahannama","kānat","mir'ṣādan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2810],[3,2810,3930],[4,3930,5895]]}},{"name":"78:22","price":"a resort for the transgressors,","arabic":"لِّلطَّٰغِينَ مَـَٔابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5694,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"lilṭṭāghīna maāban ","translations":["For the transgressors","a place of return","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["lilṭṭāghīna","maāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1660],[2,1660,3365]]}},{"name":"78:23","price":"wherein they will abide for endless ages.","arabic":"لَّٰبِثِينَ فِيهَآ أَحۡقَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5695,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"lābithīna fīhā aḥqāban ","translations":["(They will) be remaining","therein","(for) ages","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["lābithīna","fīhā","aḥqāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1370],[2,1370,3700],[3,3700,5615]]}},{"name":"78:24","price":"They will neither taste therein any coolness nor any drink,","arabic":"لَّا يَذُوقُونَ فِيهَا بَرۡدٗا وَلَا شَرَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5696,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yadhūqūna fīhā bardan walā sharāban ","translations":["Not","they will taste","therein","coolness","and not","any drink","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yadhūqūna","fīhā","bardan","walā","sharāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,520],[2,520,1890],[3,1890,2960],[4,2960,4090],[5,4090,5410],[6,5410,7245]]}},{"name":"78:25","price":"except for scalding water and discharge of wounds,","arabic":"إِلَّا حَمِيمٗا وَغَسَّاقٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5697,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"illā ḥamīman waghassāqan ","translations":["Except","scalding water","and purulence","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","ḥamīman","waghassāqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,2600],[3,2600,5185]]}},{"name":"78:26","price":"a fitting recompense[5].","arabic":"جَزَآءٗ وِفَاقًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5698,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[5] To their disbelief and evil deeds.","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"jazāan wifāqan ","translations":["A recompense","appropriate","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["jazāan","wifāqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2810],[2,2810,5025]]}},{"name":"78:27","price":"Indeed, they did not expect a reckoning,","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ لَا يَرۡجُونَ حِسَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5699,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"innahum kānū lā yarjūna ḥisāban ","translations":["Indeed, they","were","not","expecting","an account","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["innahum","kānū","lā","yarjūna","ḥisāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1540],[2,1540,2530],[3,2530,2890],[4,2890,4120],[5,4120,5955]]}},{"name":"78:28","price":"and utterly rejected Our verses.","arabic":"وَكَذَّبُواْ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا كِذَّابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5700,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wakadhabū biāyātinā kidhāban ","translations":["And they denied","Our Signs","(with) denial","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["wakadhabū","biāyātinā","kidhāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1490],[2,1490,3220],[3,3220,5505]]}},{"name":"78:29","price":"But We have enumerated everything in a record[6].","arabic":"وَكُلَّ شَيۡءٍ أَحۡصَيۡنَٰهُ كِتَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5701,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[6] i.e., a record of deeds.","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wakulla shayin aḥṣaynāhu kitāban ","translations":["And every","thing","We have enumerated it","(in) a Book","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["wakulla","shayin","aḥṣaynāhu","kitāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,2090],[3,2090,3720],[4,3720,5875]]}},{"name":"78:30","price":"So taste [the punishment], for We will not increase you except in torment[7].”","arabic":"فَذُوقُواْ فَلَن نَّزِيدَكُمۡ إِلَّا عَذَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5702,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[7] The addressees are the dwellers of Hell.","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhūqū falan nazīdakum illā ʿadhāban ","translations":["So taste","and never","We will increase you","except","(in) punishment","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhūqū","falan","nazīdakum","illā","ʿadhāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1870],[2,1870,2510],[3,2510,4700],[4,4700,5720],[5,5720,7775]]}},{"name":"78:31","price":"Indeed, the righteous will have salvation[8],","arabic":"إِنَّ لِلۡمُتَّقِينَ مَفَازًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5703,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[8] i.e., safety from Hell and winning Paradise.","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"inna lil'muttaqīna mafāzan ","translations":["Indeed","for the righteous","(is) success","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","lil'muttaqīna","mafāzan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,3250],[3,3250,4335]]}},{"name":"78:32","price":"gardens and vineyards,","arabic":"حَدَآئِقَ وَأَعۡنَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5704,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"ḥadāiqa wa-aʿnāban ","translations":["Gardens","and grapevines","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["ḥadāiqa","wa-aʿnāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2360],[2,2360,4315]]}},{"name":"78:33","price":"and full-bosomed maidens of equal age,","arabic":"وَكَوَاعِبَ أَتۡرَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5705,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wakawāʿiba atrāban ","translations":["And splendid companions","well-matched","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["wakawāʿiba","atrāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,3095]]}},{"name":"78:34","price":"and a full cup [of wine][9].","arabic":"وَكَأۡسٗا دِهَاقٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5706,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[9] i.e., tasteful wine which neither intoxicates nor causes headache.","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wakasan dihāqan ","translations":["And a cup","full","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["wakasan","dihāqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1450],[2,1450,3635]]}},{"name":"78:35","price":"They will not hear therein vain talk or lies –","arabic":"لَّا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا كِذَّٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5707,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yasmaʿūna fīhā laghwan walā kidhāban ","translations":["Not","they will hear","therein","any vain talk","and not","any falsehood","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yasmaʿūna","fīhā","laghwan","walā","kidhāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,540],[2,540,1910],[3,1910,2780],[4,2780,4460],[5,4460,4950],[6,4950,7155]]}},{"name":"78:36","price":"a reward and a generous gift from your Lord[10],","arabic":"جَزَآءٗ مِّن رَّبِّكَ عَطَآءً حِسَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5708,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[10] Or \"a gift adequately calculated\"; as a result of their righteous deeds as well as the ample generosity of Allah.","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"jazāan min rabbika ʿaṭāan ḥisāban ","translations":["(As) a reward","from","your Lord","a gift","(according to) account","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["jazāan","min","rabbika","ʿaṭāan","ḥisāban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2150],[2,2150,2880],[3,